Begin-Procedure Get-Accrual-Rate
!***********************************************************************

    !--------------------------------------------------------------------
    !--This is used to get the accrual rate from the LEAVE_PLAN_TBL     -
    !--based on the benefit plan.
    !--------------------------------------------------------------------


Begin-Select

